00:28:26.700 --> 00:28:27.780
Eventualmente...

00:28:29.980 --> 00:28:31.820
Aun así, elegiste a Thanavej.

00:28:33.500 --> 00:28:35.100
a lo largo de mi vida.

00:28:35.660 --> 00:28:36.620
Que...

